(25081, 'Potaspirono 25 mg 20 tab.', 'بوتاسبيرونو 25مجم 20 قرص', '27', '36', 'Spironolactone', 'Unipharma co.', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Diuretic.potassium-sparing diuretics', '25 mg', 'Spironolactone is indicated for the treatment of the following conditions:
