- Long-term maintenance therapy for patients with bilateral micro or macronodular adrenal hyperplasia (idiopathic hyperaldosteronism).[L44602]
As spironolactone has antiandrogenic activity, its off-label uses include the treatment of hirsutism, female pattern hair loss, and adult acne vulgaris.[A178135, A261025]', '', '', 2062, '2024-11-23', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
